contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:33.785 --> 01:35.652
Riding to work with the boss.

01:36.429 --> 01:38.293
Only four episodes deep.

01:38.293 --> 01:39.651
Oh, Rach, I think you got

01:39.651 --> 01:41.221
a little bit of Quinn on your shoe.

01:45.564 --> 01:47.095
Okay, I was running the show for Quinn.

01:47.130 --> 01:48.464
I'm running it for Coleman.

01:48.499 --> 01:50.548
Goldberg, you're sleeping
with the showrunner.

01:50.600 --> 01:51.632
Own it.

01:51.668 --> 01:53.401
Oh, my God.

01:53.437 --> 01:55.704
Babe, did you actually
shoot this with a gun?

01:55.704 --> 01:57.158
This is hilarious.

01:57.263 --> 01:58.740
You're sleeping with a contestant.

01:58.741 --> 02:00.595
And you could get kicked off for
this, by the way, young lady.

02:00.595 --> 02:01.090
Right.

02:01.090 --> 02:03.431
After you slept with the
suitor all last season?

02:03.780 --> 02:05.712
You did what?

02:05.747 --> 02:07.414
What's behind your back?

02:07.450 --> 02:08.824
Should I come take a look at it?

02:08.824 --> 02:11.151
I think I should. Let me see it.

02:11.187 --> 02:13.520
Hand it to me right now.

02:17.560 --> 02:19.025
Ah.

02:19.061 --> 02:21.794
Yep, right through my eye. That's nice.

02:21.829 --> 02:23.696
Okay. Go. Hair and makeup.

02:23.731 --> 02:24.386
Skedaddle.

02:24.386 --> 02:26.556
See you later, sweetie. Go ahead.

02:31.872 --> 02:33.193
This is wrong, okay?

02:33.193 --> 02:35.879
I'm not a 19-year-old Instagram bimbo.

02:35.879 --> 02:38.247
I am a boss. This is not what it...

02:40.181 --> 02:41.880
My God.

02:41.916 --> 02:43.048
You are a vision.

02:43.083 --> 02:45.184
And you're back.

02:45.219 --> 02:47.552
- Who bailed you out?
- Oh. Jeremy.

02:47.587 --> 02:50.255
Oh. Well, he clearly knows
where his bread is buttered.

02:50.291 --> 02:51.356
How was jail?

02:55.028 --> 02:57.361
Uh, it was hard, really hard.

02:57.396 --> 03:01.899
A lot of drunks, losers...
a lot of puke.

03:01.935 --> 03:04.668
Those are your people,
Chet, so get used to it.

03:06.372 --> 03:09.073
Um, I just wanted to say...

03:09.108 --> 03:10.741
What? You want to apologize?

03:10.776 --> 03:12.108
Beg for my forgiveness?

03:12.144 --> 03:15.045
Commit hari-kari on my rug? Go for it.

03:15.080 --> 03:17.247
I-I wanted to say that...

03:17.282 --> 03:19.615
That everything I said
before the cops came...

03:19.651 --> 03:21.184
That was... that was the truth.

03:21.220 --> 03:22.719
Well, other than the whole
"I stole my baby" thing?

03:22.754 --> 03:23.720
Yeah. Other than that.

03:24.574 --> 03:25.239
Take it off.

03:25.239 --> 03:26.260
I meant it, Quinn.

03:27.912 --> 03:29.243
You're the love of my life.

03:29.279 --> 03:30.745
Chet, stop.

03:30.781 --> 03:32.714
You're embarrassing yourself, okay?

03:32.749 --> 03:34.849
If you haven't noticed, I'm busy.

03:34.885 --> 03:36.617
I have the Impact Awards tonight, okay?

03:36.653 --> 03:39.453
I'm gonna corner John Booth,
and I'm going to produce him

03:39.489 --> 03:43.224
into letting me run one of his networks.

03:43.259 --> 03:45.193
Quinn TV.

03:45.228 --> 03:46.560
Please. John Booth.

03:46.595 --> 03:48.128
Why is it that everybody who makes

03:48.164 --> 03:49.963
a billion dollars in some other industry

03:49.999 --> 03:51.098
thinks they can run ours?

03:51.133 --> 03:52.265
He's a douche.

03:52.301 --> 03:53.701
Well, he could be.

03:53.736 --> 03:57.104
On the plus side, he's not you, Chet.

03:57.139 --> 04:00.808
And, uh, that's the
best thing about him.

04:00.843 --> 04:02.576
Ugh.

04:08.683 --> 04:10.149
Take it off.

04:10.185 --> 04:13.219
Come on, America. It's sexy time.

04:13.254 --> 04:14.987
It is your chance to
be a part of the action

04:15.023 --> 04:16.822
here on "Everlasting."

04:16.858 --> 04:20.158
Now, tonight, Darius is gonna
take things to the next level

04:20.194 --> 04:23.595
with one lucky lady
who you get to choose.

04:23.630 --> 04:24.930
Of course, we'll be
tabulating your votes

04:24.965 --> 04:26.497
as they come in throughout the show.

04:26.533 --> 04:28.166
Call, text, tweet,

04:28.202 --> 04:30.301
Snapchat, if you will, your votes

04:30.337 --> 04:33.004
for the first overnight
date of the season.

04:33.040 --> 04:37.808
And remember... America, it's
time for your voice to be heard.

04:42.014 --> 04:43.114
Oh, that's garbage.

04:43.149 --> 04:44.882
