It's been five years.

11:42.741 --> 11:44.707
I think I have a way to help us both.

11:44.743 --> 11:46.209
Really?

11:46.245 --> 11:48.344
Did you talk to the
network or talk to him or...

11:48.380 --> 11:50.546
No, no. No more shortcuts. Follow me.

11:52.884 --> 11:55.384
