said I wasn't disappointed.

11:55.419 --> 11:57.653
Yael, I was really looking forward

11:57.688 --> 12:00.189
to getting a chance to know
you a little better tonight.

12:00.224 --> 12:03.893
But considering what
I've just learned...

12:03.928 --> 12:05.928
I'm pretty sure my
heart wouldn't be in it.

12:05.963 --> 12:07.930
Can I just say, in my defense...

12:07.965 --> 12:10.298
I'm afraid Darius'
decision is final, Yael.

12:13.369 --> 12:15.336
Dominique, I'm sorry,

12:15.371 --> 12:17.071
but it's not going to be you, either.

12:17.107 --> 12:18.873
While I value monogamy and trust,

12:18.909 --> 12:21.709
I'm a big fan of
discretion and fair play,

12:21.744 --> 12:23.744
and you showed neither of those today.

12:23.780 --> 12:26.613
Who the hell is Hot
Rachel sleeping with?

12:26.648 --> 12:29.416
That said, it would be a shame

12:29.451 --> 12:31.251
to let the dream suite go to waste.

12:31.287 --> 12:35.122
I hope America won't mind
if I pick a wild card.

12:35.157 --> 12:37.357
I hate it when they go rogue.

12:37.392 --> 12:39.626
Okay.

12:39.661 --> 12:42.262
Okay, there you go. Yeah. Yeah.

12:42.298 --> 12:44.063
Stop there.

12:44.098 --> 12:46.199
Nope, nope, nope, nope.

12:46.234 --> 12:48.400
