stepped inside your brain.

27:21.363 --> 27:22.994
Quinn, this is a closed set.
What are you doing?

27:23.029 --> 27:26.265
Well, well, well, hello.

27:26.300 --> 27:28.133
Oh, good girl.

27:29.903 --> 27:32.471
Quinn, he's here.

27:32.506 --> 27:33.705
Mm. Oh, buckle up.

27:33.741 --> 27:35.574
- What, it gets better?
- Mm-hmm.

27:35.609 --> 27:37.476
Dr. Carter, welcome.

27:37.511 --> 27:39.310
No, no, no, no. You can't be here.

27:39.345 --> 27:42.079
I have been trying to reach
you people for weeks.

27:42.114 --> 27:44.214
Where's Ruby?

27:44.250 --> 27:45.650
Where's my daughter?

27:45.685 --> 27:49.520
Uh, this is a little awkward, but, um...

27:49.555 --> 27:50.988
What is this?

27:55.361 --> 27:56.726
Oh, my God.

27:56.762 --> 27:58.928
No.

28:01.791 --> 28:03.915
What the hell are you people doing?

28:04.387 --> 28:05.651
This is pornography.

28:05.687 --> 28:07.653
We're never gonna air any of this.

28:07.689 --> 28:09.622
- I mean, there's always a chance.
- Damn it.

28:09.657 --> 28:11.458
- How do I get these things off?
- Where's my daughter?

28:11.493 --> 28:12.825
Tell me now, or I call the police.

28:12.861 --> 28:14.527
Okay, calm down, Dr. Carter.

28:14.562 --> 28:15.962
I'll take you to her right away, okay?

28:15.998 --> 28:17.763
Sit tight. Make us some drinks.

28:17.799 --> 28:20.133
Madison, cameras up
outside my office now.

28:20.168 --> 28:22.767
Cameras up outside of
Quinn's office right now.

28:24.838 --> 28:25.971
Where are you?

28:26.007 --> 28:27.601
It's right this way.

28:27.601 --> 28:28.243
Rach.

28:28.267 --> 28:30.209
Honestly, you couldn't
keep him out of there?

28:30.211 --> 28:31.543
He was already here before I knew.

28:31.578 --> 28:34.179
What was I... No. No, no, no, no, no.

28:34.215 --> 28:36.348
No, no, no, no. Hey, guys, cameras down.

28:36.384 --> 28:38.350
Guys, let's keep those cameras
down. Guys, cameras down!

28:38.386 --> 28:39.550
- Mr. Carter, stop. Stop. Stop.
- Seriously.

28:39.585 --> 28:41.119
Please stop.

28:41.988 --> 28:43.554
- Ruby. Oh.
- Dad?

28:43.589 --> 28:44.788
Oh, my God.

28:44.824 --> 28:46.290
Please, let's get out of here.

28:46.326 --> 28:48.493
- Your dad?
- What are you doing here?

28:48.528 --> 28:49.105
Honestly?

28:49.129 --> 28:50.062
- What are you doing?
- Get in there. Get in there.

28:50.063 --> 28:51.695
No, don't go in... Don't get in there.

28:51.731 --> 28:53.364
Don't go anywhere. No,
no, no. Stay right there.

28:53.400 --> 28:55.166
Don't go in there. Don't.
Seriously. Yeah, sit there.

28:55.201 --> 28:56.192
You can't help yourself,
can you, Quinn, huh?

28:56.192 --> 28:56.914
I want security down here.

28:56.914 --> 28:58.218
- I want Ruby's dad out of here.
- Fine.

28:59.005 --> 29:00.604
You can shut this down.

29:00.640 --> 29:04.307
And you can produce a sad,
boring little NPR morality play.

29:04.343 --> 29:07.325
Or you can let this be the
great piece of television

29:07.325 --> 29:08.771
- that you know that it is.
- What are you doing?

29:08.771 --> 29:10.781
You know you want to tell that story.

29:10.816 --> 29:14.651
This is who you are, Rachel,
and this is what we love to do.

29:14.686 --> 29:16.119
You're coming with me.

29:16.154 --> 29:17.353
Mr. Carter, step outside, please.

29:17.388 --> 29:18.688
How could you let him in here?

29:18.723 --> 29:20.422
Somebody do something.

29:20.458 --> 29:21.991
I will carry you out of
here on my back if I have to.

29:22.027 --> 29:23.826
- Please.
- Do you have any idea

29:23.862 --> 29:26.462
of the impact this will
have on our foundation?

29:28.800 --> 29:29.765
All right, come on. Let's go.

29:29.800 --> 29:32.367
Rachel, no. No.

29:32.402 --> 29:34.536
Rach, no.

29:34.571 --> 29:37.605
No, no, no, no, no. I said
get that camera out of here!

29:37.641 --> 29:39.374
No. Get out. Get out. Get
that camera out of here.

29:39.409 --> 29:41.276
17 million people will be watching this.

29:41.311 --> 29:43.645
- Keep this cool. Keep it cool, okay?
- Get them out of here.

29:43.681 --> 29:45.881
You go ahead. Tell your daughter
what you want her to hear.

29:54.824 --> 29:57.624
You've worked so hard... MENSA at 16,

29:57.660 --> 29:59.160
Phi Beta Kappa for this?

29:59.195 --> 30:00.895
- None of that's changed.
- It's all changed.

30:00.930 --> 30:02.863
Whenever someone Googles you now,

30:02.899 --> 30:04.630
the first thing that'll
come up is this show.

30:04.666 --> 30:06.199
Daddy, I came on this show to have

30:06.234 --> 30:08.334
a wider platform for
what we're trying to say.

30:08.369 --> 30:10.103
Then how did you end up here?

30:11.239 --> 30:12.605
I fell in love.

30:13.942 --> 30:15.474
Oh, my God.

30:15.510 --> 30:17.243
Love after four weeks on a reality show?

30:17.278 --> 30:18.745
What the hell's gotten into you?

30:18.780 --> 30:21.046
He's a pro football player, Ruby.

30:21.082 --> 30:23.048
- I make $40 million a year.
- Dad, you don't even know him.

30:23.084 --> 30:25.517
I know all I need to know.
Bitch, please.

30:25.552 --> 30:26.819
Dad, you're making a fool of yourself.

30:26.854 --> 30:28.587
No, he is!

30:28.622 --> 30:32.024
To be where he is, in his position,

30:32.059 --> 30:34.226
and not doing more for his people.

30:34.261 --> 30:36.261
- Dr. Carter...
- Please, can we just talk?

30:36.296 --> 30:37.762
Once you leave here, sweetheart,

30:37.797 --> 30:39.197
