30:46.206 --> 30:49.207
I'm sorry, Dad, but I'm staying here.

30:58.117 --> 30:59.850
I'm so ashamed of you.

31:23.741 --> 31:25.540
Wow. Hell of a show.

31:25.576 --> 31:26.742
You don't mess around.

31:26.778 --> 31:28.477
Sometimes you just get lucky.

31:28.512 --> 31:31.279
Mm. I don't believe that for a second.

31:31.314 --> 31:33.248
I think you're just like me.

31:33.283 --> 31:35.750
We make our own luck.

31:35.786 --> 31:39.420
Now, I always thought this
was scripted or made up.

31:39.455 --> 31:42.490
Oh, we don't make it up.
We make it happen.

31:42.525 --> 31:44.425
Well, to the master of disaster.

31:44.460 --> 31:47.327
Ah. Hmm.

31:47.362 --> 31:51.631
Uh, Jay, Madison, wake the girls up.

31:51.667 --> 31:53.233
We're having an elimination ceremony.

31:54.837 --> 31:56.103
Quinn, it's almost midnight.

31:56.138 --> 31:57.905
I don't care how late it is.

31:57.940 --> 32:00.740
And if I see one
droopy eye or saggy tit,

32:00.776 --> 32:02.276
someone's getting fired.

32:05.446 --> 32:07.680
Why don't you go outside
and meet the girls

32:07.715 --> 32:09.415
while I get this thing ready?

32:09.450 --> 32:11.517
- Can I meet Beth Ann?
- Sure.

32:11.552 --> 32:13.085
She might even say the "N" word for you.

32:13.121 --> 32:15.587
The set's right around the corner.

32:24.865 --> 32:25.931
What the hell is wrong with you?

32:25.966 --> 32:27.432
You sent in her father?

32:27.467 --> 32:30.297
Yeah, and you sent in
the camera after him.

32:30.297 --> 32:30.601
