32:33.707 --> 32:35.273
that you weren't invited to the party,

32:35.309 --> 32:36.774
and so you're taking it out on Ruby.

32:36.810 --> 32:38.375
Oh, don't kid yourself, Rachel.

32:38.410 --> 32:40.110
I am always invited to the party.

32:40.146 --> 32:41.478
The only reason why you went

32:41.513 --> 32:43.113
is because you're banging the boss.

32:43.149 --> 32:44.614
Well, I learned from the best.

32:44.650 --> 32:46.683
You think Coleman's
your ticket out of here?

32:46.719 --> 32:47.223
Please.

32:47.223 --> 32:49.686
You could run circles around
that snot-nosed little brat.

32:49.722 --> 32:51.188
You're just too scared to.

32:51.224 --> 32:52.789
You know something? I am not scared.

32:52.825 --> 32:55.225
For the first time in my life,
I actually have a partner.

32:55.260 --> 32:56.692
Wha... He's not your partner.

32:56.728 --> 32:58.828
He's your Chet, okay?

32:58.864 --> 33:01.759
He's gonna steal all of your
ideas and take the credit.

33:01.759 --> 33:03.032
Nope. Coleman is not Chet.

33:03.068 --> 33:05.034
Yes, he is, but you're not me.

33:05.070 --> 33:07.036
You're not gonna survive it, okay?

33:07.072 --> 33:08.571
You're gonna be right back
to sleeping in your car

33:08.606 --> 33:10.006
and snorting cold
medicine for breakfast.

33:10.041 --> 33:13.075
Okay, let me paint you
a very different picture.

33:13.110 --> 33:14.509
In three years,

33:14.544 --> 33:16.778
I will have my own show
and a man that loves me.

33:17.748 --> 33:20.082
Okay, I am just trying
to protect you, Rachel.

33:20.117 --> 33:22.851
From what, the beautiful
life that you never had?

33:22.887 --> 33:24.019
No, thanks.

33:24.054 --> 33:25.387
He's a user.

33:25.422 --> 33:29.690
Just... be careful, okay?

33:41.748 --> 33:43.747
Hey.

33:44.283 --> 33:47.850
I am so sorry about my father.

33:47.886 --> 33:50.420
Hey, not the first time a
girl's dad walked in on me.

33:50.455 --> 33:54.090
Well, first time since
high school maybe.

34:00.932 --> 34:03.098
I know he's your dad, okay, but...

34:03.133 --> 34:04.933
He can be an ass.

34:04.968 --> 34:09.804
Mnh. Not quite the word
I was gonna use, but...

34:09.840 --> 34:11.540
The things he said...

34:11.576 --> 34:13.542
He was just surprised and angry and...

34:13.578 --> 34:17.079
Yeah, but he wasn't wrong,
not about all of it.

34:18.181 --> 34:20.281
This might sound crazy to you,

34:20.317 --> 34:23.384
but I know that I was put on
this earth to make a difference,

34:23.420 --> 34:24.918
to be heard, and...

34:24.954 --> 34:27.589
And not to fall for a
dumb-ass football player.

34:27.623 --> 34:28.755
But you're more than that.

34:28.791 --> 34:30.407
I don't know, Ruby.

34:30.407 --> 34:31.246
Yeah, but
you said...

34:33.496 --> 34:35.661
Well, don't you want to be?

34:35.697 --> 34:38.498
You can do more.

34:38.534 --> 34:39.766
You could speak up.

34:39.801 --> 34:41.967
I could teach you.

34:42.003 --> 34:45.438
You can be everything my
father says that you're not.

34:45.474 --> 34:47.574
You know that, right?

34:47.610 --> 34:49.943
Yeah.

34:49.978 --> 34:51.445
I know that.

35:17.170 --> 35:21.172
Ladies, obviously it's, uh...
It's been a very long night.

35:21.207 --> 35:23.708
But for one of you, it is about to end.

35:23.744 --> 35:27.144
If your candle is extinguished,
it is time to say goodbye.

35:27.179 --> 35:31.882
Darius, before you say anything...

35:31.917 --> 35:33.550
I need to apologize

35:33.586 --> 35:36.587
for the dirty, disgusting
mistakes I've made.

35:36.622 --> 35:40.824
"Mistakes." You hear that?
That's plural.

35:40.859 --> 35:42.326
I did something beneath me.

35:42.361 --> 35:45.861
Yael, stop.

35:45.897 --> 35:47.430
I'm not here to judge anybody.

35:47.465 --> 35:50.833
Um... actually, yes, you...
You are here to judge us.

35:50.868 --> 35:52.669
We are all human.

35:52.704 --> 35:54.537
We all make mistakes.

35:54.572 --> 35:56.539
The best we can do is learn from them.

35:56.574 --> 35:58.675
You're safe tonight, Yael.

36:00.377 --> 36:02.377
Oh, my...

36:04.080 --> 36:06.014
Dominique.

36:06.049 --> 36:08.550
Seriously? Me?

36:08.585 --> 36:10.218
All I did was to tell you the truth.

36:10.253 --> 36:11.720
So that you could bring
somebody else down.

36:11.755 --> 36:14.222
Come on! Is this a joke?

36:14.257 --> 36:15.557
