36:15.592 --> 36:17.891
You know, I'm getting a little tired

36:17.927 --> 36:20.060
of being told what I can and can't do.

36:28.103 --> 36:29.437
Camera A, follow her.

36:29.472 --> 36:31.104
Wow. Tough night, huh?

36:31.140 --> 36:32.807
I'm not done. I got one more.

36:32.842 --> 36:35.608
He's going off book, ladies.
Darius is calling an audible.

36:35.644 --> 36:38.211
No. No. No, no, no.

36:38.246 --> 36:39.646
What are you doing?

36:39.681 --> 36:41.314
No, no, no, no.

36:41.350 --> 36:44.784
I'm sorry, Ruby, but your dad was right.

36:44.820 --> 36:48.087
You've got a lot of important
work ahead of you.

36:48.122 --> 36:49.489
