36:49.524 --> 36:52.924
Look. Whoever it is
you think I could be...

36:52.960 --> 36:54.493
you should go be with that guy.

36:54.528 --> 36:55.661
No.

36:55.696 --> 36:57.128
Darius, that's not what I meant.

36:57.164 --> 36:59.264
Okay. Maybe I could do more.

36:59.299 --> 37:01.115
I'm not saying you're wrong.

37:01.115 --> 37:01.767
I'm just saying

37:01.802 --> 37:06.137
I don't feel like I'm
enough for you or your dad.

37:08.208 --> 37:09.974
And I don't like how that feels.

37:10.009 --> 37:12.243
Darius, please.

37:12.278 --> 37:13.911
