37:13.946 --> 37:16.313
disappointing you every day, Ruby.

37:30.562 --> 37:32.161
I can't believe I trusted you.

37:32.197 --> 37:33.930
Jay, I did everything I could.

37:37.503 --> 37:39.202
Ladies, uh, that concludes

37:39.237 --> 37:41.438
our elimination ceremony this evening.

37:42.340 --> 37:44.440
Good night.

37:46.644 --> 37:52.180
Well, did you, uh, see
everything you needed to see?

37:52.216 --> 37:53.916
