38:10.400 --> 38:12.199
Don't you have three or four?

38:12.235 --> 38:14.469
Six. No, seven.

38:14.504 --> 38:15.804
You can choose.

38:15.839 --> 38:21.341
I would, but I have this thing tomorrow.

38:21.376 --> 38:23.143
Well, that sounds incredibly vague.

38:24.613 --> 38:27.180
My dad died.

38:27.215 --> 38:28.549
Funeral's tomorrow.

38:28.584 --> 38:30.183
